## Source Code

The source code in this repository is made publicly available solely for
educational and presentation (portfolio) purposes. You may review the code, learn
from it, and draw inspiration from the technical solutions used.

The following is NOT permitted without the author’s express written consent:
- Copying all or a significant portion of the code to create your own
  commercial or non-commercial product
- Deploying this code (or its derivatives) in production for another entity
- Distributing this code as part of another project or template

The following is permitted:
- Reviewing the code for educational purposes
- Drawing inspiration from general architectural patterns and technical approaches
- Forking the repository solely for local learning purposes (without publishing
  your own, functioning copy of the website)

